items.name: SLT Strategic Priorities for AI Adoption

columns.What are your top business needs or chal: Defining the scope of AI initiatives, prioritizing business impact, and managing risks and costs for successful rollout.
columns.Which types of AI initiatives would be m: Process Automation, Data Analysis & Insight Generation
columns.From a leadership perspective, what are: Establishing clear objectives, building confidence in implementation, and developing a roadmap with measurable outcomes.

columns.What are your top business needs or chal: Building foundational AI knowledge and awareness, addressing skill limitations, and sharing knowledge across the business.
columns.What are the main barriers or considerat: Skill Limitations, Technical Requirements, Change Management

columns.What are your top business needs or chal: Selecting AI tools that balance cost, security, and data integrity for organization-wide deployment.
columns.From a leadership perspective, what are: Establishing robust evaluation criteria and minimizing risks associated with new AI tools.

columns.What are your top business needs or chal: We need to improve impact analysis on asset utilization and gain deeper insights into asset performance and time management.
columns.Which types of AI initiatives would be m: Data Analysis & Insight Generation, Process Automation
columns.From a leadership perspective, what are: Our top priorities are improving operational efficiency, increasing asset ROI, and building a roadmap for scalable AI deployment.
columns.Are there specific AI tools or platforms: Power BI, Tableau AI, AWS AI Services

columns.What are your top business needs or chal: Automating influencer selection, monitoring downtimes, detecting dead links, and managing out-of-stock situations across major channels.
columns.Which types of AI initiatives would be m: Issue Detection (e.g., downtime, dead links), Process Automation, Marketing Optimization
columns.What are the main barriers or considerat: Data Integrity, Change Management, Local Impact
columns.From a leadership perspective, what are: Ensuring reliable channel execution, quick issue identification, and minimizing business disruption.

columns.Business Need or AI Opportunity Title: Establish Weekly Call and Knowledge Bank Workflows
columns.Describe the business need or AI opportu: Create a structured weekly call, pre-read process, and a system for collating discussions into a searchable knowledge bank for committee operations.
columns.What are the main objectives or expected: Enhance committee coordination, ensure effective communication, and build a central repository of discussions and decisions.
columns.Are there known risks, dependencies, or: Requires commitment from all committee members for participation and documentation.

columns.Business Need or AI Opportunity Title: Build AI Knowledge and Awareness Across Staff
columns.Describe the business need or AI opportu: Develop educational materials, technical requirements, and staff surveys to establish a baseline of AI understanding and identify knowledge gaps.
columns.What are the main objectives or expected: Increase AI literacy, reduce skill limitations, and prepare staff for AI-driven transformation.
columns.Are there known risks, dependencies, or: Staff engagement and effective content delivery are critical to success.

items.name: SLT AI Priorities and Scope Definition

columns.Business Need or AI Opportunity Title: Define SLT AI Objectives and Project Scope Framework
columns.Describe the business need or AI opportu: Gather SLT input on AI priorities, structure questions, and define a framework for scoping AI projects (time, impact, confidence, cost, security, speed to MVP, cost/benefit, risks).
columns.Which areas does this need impact?: Global Impact, Revenue Growth, Risk Reduction
columns.What are the main objectives or expected: Align AI initiatives with SLT priorities, standardize project scoping, and improve decision-making.
columns.Are there known risks, dependencies, or: Requires timely input from SLT and agreement on scope criteria.

items.name: Tool Evaluation: Cost, Security, and Data Integrity

columns.Describe the business need or AI opportu: Establish a standardized framework for evaluating AI tools with a focus on cost, security, and data integrity to guide committee decisions.
columns.What are the main objectives or expected: Ensure consistent, transparent, and risk-aware tool selection and deployment across the organization.
columns.Are there known risks, dependencies, or: Alignment on evaluation criteria and stakeholder buy-in may require additional effort.

items.name: Asset Performance Insights for IM Analysis

columns.Business Need or AI Opportunity Title: Enhance Asset and Time Impact Analysis
columns.Describe the business need or AI opportu: Develop advanced analytics to provide deeper insight into asset performance, downtime, and time impact to optimize utilization and business value.
columns.Which areas does this need impact?: Operational Efficiency, Revenue Growth, Local Impact
columns.What are the main objectives or expected: Reduce asset downtime, improve resource allocation, and increase overall operational efficiency by leveraging AI-driven insights.
columns.Are there known risks, dependencies, or: Data quality and integration with legacy systems may present challenges.

columns.Business Need or AI Opportunity Title: Automated Detection of Downtimes and Dead Links
columns.Describe the business need or AI opportu: Implement AI solutions to automatically identify and report downtimes, dead links, and out-of-stock items across major sales channels.
columns.Which areas does this need impact?: Customer Experience, Risk Reduction, Global Impact
columns.What are the main objectives or expected: Minimize lost sales opportunities, improve uptime, and proactively address channel issues to enhance customer satisfaction.
columns.Key considerations for this need: Speed to MVP, Technical Requirements, Skill Limitations
columns.Are there known risks, dependencies, or: Requires integration with multiple platforms and real-time data feeds.
